<style>
.jewelry-care-section { margin-top: var(--margin-top-desktop) !important; margin-bottom: var(--margin-bottom-desktop) !important; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; max-width:1180px !important; }
.jewelry-care-heading{font-weight:500;font-size:32px;line-height:150%;letter-spacing:4%;text-transform:uppercase;color:#1a1a1a;margin:0}
.jewelry-care-paragraph p{font-weight:400;font-size:18px;line-height:24px;letter-spacing:4%;color:#1a1a1a;margin:0}
@media screen and (max-width:768px){
.jewelry-care-section{margin-top:var(--margin-top-mobile)!important;margin-bottom:var(--margin-bottom-mobile)!important;gap:12px}
.jewelry-care-heading{font-size:21px}
.jewelry-care-paragraph p{font-size:12px;line-height:18px}
}
</style>

<section
  class="jewelry-care-section page-width"
  style="
    --margin-top-desktop: {{ section.settings.margin_top_desktop | default: 0 }}px;
    --margin-bottom-desktop: {{ section.settings.margin_bottom_desktop | default: 0 }}px;
    --margin-top-mobile: {{ section.settings.margin_top_mobile | default: 0 }}px;
    --margin-bottom-mobile: {{ section.settings.margin_bottom_mobile | default: 0 }}px;
  "
>
  <h2 class="jewelry-care-heading">
    {{ section.settings.heading }}
  </h2>

  <div class="jewelry-care-paragraph">
    {{ section.settings.paragraph1 }}
  </div>

  <div class="jewelry-care-paragraph">
    {{ section.settings.paragraph2 }}
  </div>
</section>



{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Tips To Follow",
  "tag": "section",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "heading",
      "label": "Heading",
      "default": "What are the best jewelry care tips to follow?"
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "paragraph1",
      "label": "Paragraph 1",
      "default": "<p>Ever wondered how, in Bollywood movies, jewelry keeps its sparkle even after being passed down for generations? The secret lies in premium quality and proper care. We, at Luciria, craft your jewelry with the finest materials and design our pieces to last for lifetimes but even the best jewelry needs a little care to maintain its brilliance.</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "paragraph2",
      "label": "Paragraph 2",
      "default": "<p>In this guide, we include daily tips for your everyday jewelry, how to store jewelry, and how to tackle some common jewelry problems like tangled necklaces. Read more about material specific care here.</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "margin_top_desktop",
      "label": "Desktop Margin Top",
      "min": 0,
      "max": 200,
      "step": 4,
      "unit": "px",
      "default": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "margin_bottom_desktop",
      "label": "Desktop Margin Bottom",
      "min": 0,
      "max": 200,
      "step": 4,
      "unit": "px",
      "default": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "margin_top_mobile",
      "label": "Mobile Margin Top",
      "min": 0,
      "max": 200,
      "step": 4,
      "unit": "px",
      "default": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "margin_bottom_mobile",
      "label": "Mobile Margin Bottom",
      "min": 0,
      "max": 200,
      "step": 4,
      "unit": "px",
      "default": 0
    }
  ],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "Tips To Follow",
      "category": "Custom"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
